content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/NergalSkills.png 673w, https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/NergalSkills-300x247.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 673px) 100vw, 673px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><em>*Death &amp; Decay is a spell that casts at the location on the battlefield in which the allied panther unit was killed. The effect is similar to that of the Poison Cloud spell, but with +400% damage, +50% increase to the area of effect (radius), and +50% increase in duration<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>**Each Warrior Spirit is an incarnation of Nergal himself, but with 50% Health and Damage of Nergal\u2019s base stats at Level 60 (At Prestige 10). At each reduction of Nergal\u2019s total health by 30% (i.e. when 70%, 40% and 10% health remain), a Warrior Spirit will be summoned into battle on a random enemy troop location. These spirits act as a Poison Element Titan that can not only be controlled in battle, but also buffed by existing Relic and Skill effects that boost Poison Titan stats.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/WszFWux0kmrecTW9Byc-SM5DbN61ia0sF_zlUdlrxAqfmPikEcvd8kYmu2sX8Vm_yU_jjBf-JTDqoZM4R21ENGfJ7q0bWs5CAddUyr_JRsXe7J2DF7W8TytyrK6cjBjbd0Hh1INl\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Get these<strong> powerful Relics and more <\/strong>in the Milestone Rewards:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"440\" height=\"436\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Nergal_KhanjarSynergy.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1336\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Nergal_KhanjarSynergy.png 440w, https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Nergal_KhanjarSynergy-300x297.png 300w, https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Nergal_KhanjarSynergy-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-wi